Package it.polimi.ingsw.am49.common.util

Class BiMap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am49.common.util.BiMap<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - the type of keys maintained by this map
V - the type of mapped values
public class BiMap<K,V> extends Object
The BiMap class represents a bidirectional map that maintains a one-to-one relationship between keys and values. It allows for efficient lookups from keys to values and values to keys.
